rect">1st Loc Ninh</a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Dak_To" title="Battle of Dak To">Dak To</a> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_in_the_Mekong_Delta&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle in the Mekong Delta (page does not exist)">Mekong Delta</a> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_of_Tam_Quan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle of Tam Quan (page does not exist)">Tam Quan</a> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_of_Thom_Tham_Khe&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle of Thom Tham Khe (page does not exist)">Thom Tham Khe</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/Phoenix_Program" title="Phoenix Program">Phoenix</a></i> – <a href="/wiki/Siege_of_Khe_Sanh" title="Siege of Khe Sanh" class="mw-redirect">Khe Sanh</a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Ban_Houei_Sane" title="Battle of Ban Houei Sane">Ban Houei Sane</a> – <a href="/wiki/Tet_Offensive" title="Tet Offensive">1st Tet</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/First_Battle_of_Saigon" title="First Battle of Saigon">1st Saigon</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Hu%E1%BA%BF" title="Battle of Huế">Huế</a>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_of_Bien_Hoa&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle of Bien Hoa (page does not exist)">Bien Hoa</a> – <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Lang_Vei" title="Battle of Lang Vei">Lang Vei</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Lima_Site_85" title="Battle of Lima Site 85">Lima Site 85</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Delaware" title="Operation Delaware">Delaware</a></i> – <a href="/w/index.php?title=Second_Battle_of_Dong_Ha&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Second Battle of Dong Ha (page does not exist)">2nd Dong Ha</a> – <i><a href="/wiki/May_Offensive" title="May Offensive">May '68</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Kham_Duc" title="Battle of Kham Duc">Kham Duc</a>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Battle_of_Duc_Lap&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Battle of Duc Lap (page does not exist)">Duc Lap</a>&#160;– <i>