>FSB Ripcord</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Tailwind" title="Operation Tailwind">Tailwind</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Chenla_I" title="Operation Chenla I">Chenla I</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Jefferson_Glenn" title="Operation Jefferson Glenn">Jefferson Glenn</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Ivory_Coast" title="Operation Ivory Coast">Son Tay Raid</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Lam_Son_719" title="Operation Lam Son 719">Lam Son 719</a></i>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_Chenla_II" title="Operation Chenla II">Chenla II</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Ban_Dong" title="Battle of Ban Dong">Ban Dong</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Hill_723" title="Battle of Hill 723">Hill 723</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_FSB_Mary_Ann" title="Battle of FSB Mary Ann">FSB Mary Ann</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Easter_Offensive" title="Easter Offensive">Easter '72</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/First_Battle_of_Qu%E1%BA%A3ng_Tr%E1%BB%8B" title="First Battle of Quảng Trị">1st Quảng Trị</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Loc_Ninh" title="Battle of Loc Ninh">2nd Loc Ninh</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_An_L%E1%BB%99c" title="Battle of An Lộc">An Lộc</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng_H%E1%BB%9Bi" title="Battle of Đồng Hới">Đồng Hới</a>&#160;– <a href="/w/index.php?title=Third_Battle_of_Dong_Ha&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Third Battle of Dong Ha (page does not exist)">3rd Dong Ha</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Kontum" title="Battle of Kontum">Kontum</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Second_Battle_of_Qu%E1%BA%A3ng_Tr%E1%BB%8B" title="Second Battle of Quảng Trị">2nd Quảng Trị</a>&#160;– <i><a href="/wiki/Operation_End_Sweep" title="Operation End Sweep">End Sweep</a></i>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Hoang_Sa" title="Battle of Hoang Sa" class="mw-redirect">Hoang Sa</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_the_Iron_Triangle" title="Battle of the Iron Triangle">Iron Triangle</a>&#160;– <a hr