<p><b><a href="/wiki/Aerial_warfare#Vietnam_War" title="Aerial warfare">Air operations</a></b><br />
<i><a href="/wiki/Farm_Gate" title="Farm Gate">Farm Gate</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Chopper" title="Operation Chopper">Chopper</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Ranch_Hand" title="Operation Ranch Hand">Ranch Hand</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Pierce_Arrow" title="Operation Pierce Arrow">Pierce Arrow</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Barrel_Roll" title="Operation Barrel Roll">Barrel Roll</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Pony_Express" title="Operation Pony Express">Pony Express</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Flaming_Dart" title="Operation Flaming Dart">Flaming Dart</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Rolling_Thunder" title="Operation Rolling Thunder">Rolling Thunder</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Steel_Tiger" title="Operation Steel Tiger">Steel Tiger</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Arc_Light" title="Operation Arc Light">Arc Light</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Tiger_Hound" title="Operation Tiger Hound">Tiger Hound</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Shed_Light" title="Operation Shed Light">Shed Light</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Carolina_Moon" title="Operation Carolina Moon" class="mw-redirect">Carolina Moon</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Bolo" title="Operation Bolo">Bolo</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Popeye" title="Operation Popeye">Popeye</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Niagara" title="Operation Niagara">Niagara</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Igloo_White" title="Operation Igloo White">Igloo White</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Giant_Lance" title="Operation Giant Lance">Giant Lance</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Commando_Hunt" title="Operation Commando Hunt">Commando Hunt</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Menu" title="Operation Menu">Menu</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Patio" title="Operation Patio">Patio</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Freedom_Deal" title="Operation Freedom Deal">Freedom Deal</a> – <a href="/wiki/Operation_Linebacker" title="Operation Linebacker">Linebacker I</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Enhance_Plus" title="Operation Enhance Plus">Enhance Plus</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Linebacker_II" title="Operation Linebacker II">Linebacker II</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Homecoming" title="Operation Homecoming">Homecoming</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Baby_Lift" title="Operation Baby Lift" class="mw-redirect">Baby Lift</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Eagle_Pull" title="Operation Eagle Pull">Eagle Pull</a>&#160;– <a href="/wiki/Operation_Frequent_Wind" title="Operation Frequent Wind">Frequent Wind</a></i></p>
