</ul>
<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Gulf_of_Tonkin_Incident&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> Edwin E. Moise, <i>Tonkin Gulf</i></li>
<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <strong class="selflink"><i>LBJ tape 'confirms Vietnam war error',</i> Martin Fletcher, The Times, November 7th, 2001</strong></li>
